==English==
===Etymology===
From Latin exquadrare, to square off, via Spanish esquadra, a squadron, and esquadrilla, a small squadron

===Noun===
'''escadrille'''


# A small squadron
# A WWI squadron of six aeroplanes in the French Airforce

